            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Descriptions are the primary mechanism for teaching Claude when and how to use a tool \u2014 invest as much care in them as in function docstrings."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Generate schemas programmatically from Python type hints or Pydantic models to keep definitions in sync with implementations."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Always validate generated arguments server-side \u2014 JSON Schema constraints in "
                  },
                  {
